      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm looking to find a new home for my trusty car! It\u2019s been such a reliable ride for me and is still in really solid shape. It\u2019s perfect for someone who wants a dependable vehicle without the 'brand new' price tag. It\u2019s got plenty of life left in it and is ready for its next big adventure! Feel free to message me with any questions\u2014I'd love to chat and tell you more about it! \u2728",
