    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This 2018 Porsche Macan S is a meticulously cared-for example that perfectly balances daily utility with Porsche's signature performance. Finished in Volcano Grey Metallic, the exterior retains a deep, mirror-like gloss; while the body is straight and free of major blemishes, minor stone chips on the front fascia are present, consistent with responsible highway use. The 19-inch Macan Design wheels are free of curb rash and are currently wrapped in Michelin Latitude Sport 3 tires with approximately 70% tread remaining. Inside, the Agate Grey leather interior has been regularly conditioned; the seats remain firm, the bolsters show only minimal signs of entry/exit wear, and the cabin is a strictly smoke-free environment. Every technological feature, including the Porsche Communication Management (PCM) navigation and the multi-zone climate control, functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, the vehicle is robust, having followed a strict maintenance schedule at authorized service centers. The 3.0L V6 twin-turbo engine delivers power smoothly, and the 7-speed PDK transmission shifts with crisp precision. Recent service included an oil change and a multi-point inspection, confirming the brakes and suspension are in solid working order. This vehicle comes with a complete set of owner\u2019s manuals, two keys, and a clean title.",
